{"about_the_game":"Introducing Mana Cycle, the ultimate puzzle party game experience! Dive into a digital world of strategic block-dropping madness where strategy and reflexes collide. Mana Cycle offers a fresh twist on the classic falling block puzzle genre, combining elements of Tetris and Puyo-Puyo with its own unique mechanics.<br>This game introduces the &quot;Cycle&quot; mechanic, presenting players with an order that the pieces must be cleared (&quot;spellcasted&quot;) in. Strategize your moves carefully as you clear pieces according to the ever-rotating cycle in the center of the screen. Features 7 playable characters, each with unique abilities.<br><br>Settle into a variety of engaging game modes: <br>-<strong>Story Mode</strong>, where you embark on a journey through puzzle-filled landscapes. <br>-Challenge your limits in the <strong>Endless</strong> gamemode, dropping pieces for as long as you can. <br>-Test your skills in the <strong>Arcade</strong> mode against a continuous onslaught of opponents.<br>-Brave the unpredictable depths of the roguelite-inspired <strong>Gauntlet </strong> gamemode.<br>-Hone your PvP skills against challenging AI opponents in local <strong>Player vs. CPU</strong> versus matches.<br>-Challenge your friends in local multiplayer, either via the same keyboard or via controllers.<br><br>Prepare for the ultimate puzzle showdown with Mana Cycle. Are you ready to master the art of the cycle?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Shadow Wizard Mana Caster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2864390/ef01c2f74d2932fa440c8917dbbcac10c1e25435.jpg"},{"name":"IBN Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2864390/a50d4f2c9702ec8bf8a9a53946d9151368f7deaf.jpg"},{"name":"Undefeatable, probably","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2864390/e18437c0aa401661fca4a64d01d85bbe843a5b11.jpg"},{"name":"Uncapturable, probably","